}, {\"sentence\": \"Little did the pair, who shook hands after the interaction, know that six hours later on the second ascent of three up the fabled hill to Montmartre, it would be the two riders they had wanted,Remco Evenepoeland Valentin Madouas, who were at the front of the bike race for Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.892351370393475e-53, \"text\": \"Montmartre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"hands\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"the interaction\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the second ascent\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"three up the fabled hill\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"the two riders\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"Remco Evenepoeland Valentin Madouas\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike race\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chants of \\\"Allez Remco!\\\"\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chants\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"Allez Remco\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and \\\"Allez Valentin!\\\"\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"and \\\"Allez Valentin\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"merged into one as they flew by me towards the Rue Norvins and the wall of fans who lined the steps and bank in front of the Sacr\\u00e9-C\\u0153er Basilica with 28km to go.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Rue Norvins\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the steps\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"bank\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sacr\\u00e9-C\\u0153er Basilica\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"28km\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it was later confirmed to be a 500,000-strong crowd that lined the streets of Paris, I was among the thousands crammed onto Rue Lepic, who crowded around the nearest phone streaming the race amid the patchy mobile data, to try and see how things would unfold before the final ascent to Montmartre.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.345264203563413e-56, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rue_Lepic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rue Lepic\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rue_Lepic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rue_Lepic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 500,000-strong crowd\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"the thousands\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"the nearest phone streaming\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"the patchy mobile data\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"the final ascent\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"Montmartre\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At different in